text: A painting thought to be of Thomas Seele. Unknown artist. Oil on canvas. Thomas Seele (c. 1611-1675) was an Irish Anglican, dean of St Patrick's Cathedral, and Provost of Trinity College Dublin from 1661 to 1675.Thomas Seele. Trinity College Dublin.
